headline.main: Wildfires Cause Weekend of Road Closures Across Florida
headline.print_headline: Wildfires Cause Weekend of Road Closures Across Florida

lead_paragraph: Officials say at least one large brush fire is still burning in South Florida following a weekend of road closures across the state.
